OL,3,CProgramme listings for THU 5 MAR
OL,4,G2240FMark Lawson Talks to Stephen King
OL,5,     GMaster of horror writing Stephen
OL,6,     GKing talks to Mark Lawson about
OL,7,     Ghis book Lisey's Story and
OL,8,     Gdiscusses the inspiration for his
OL,9,     Gnovels and how he battled with
OL,10,     Ghis own demons.
OL,11,G2340FLight and Dark
OL,12,     GProfessor Jim Al-Khalili shows
OL,13,     Ghow mathematicians and scientists
OL,14,     Gsuch as Euclid, Galileo and Ole
OL,15,     GRoemer have used light to reveal
OL,16,     Galmost everything we know about
OL,17,     Gthe universe.
OL,18,G0040FRomancing the Stone: The Golden
OL,19,     FAges of British Sculpture
OL,20,     GAlastair Sooke looks at the 20th
OL,21,     Gcentury's mixture of innovation,
OL,22,     Gscandal and creativity.
